*Ormund Valley*

*The Greying Pines*
Medium sized forest just north of Ironside.
Known for it's pines with pale bark, hence the name.
Brief site of the the Goliath camp.
Home of Nym - a "Guardian Nymph" of the forest, who gave Tod the band of Nym

